_sText:
If you want to create a new version of this map, then contact Xquality for more info.

Improvements: Now there's a fourth boss; Frog-dog! Fixed some hp on bosses and balanced some stuff.
Also fixed the Loo from exploding by dead dogs.

Frog-dog Fixed.

You have to survive for 10 minutes - I've heard rumors about this map being unbeatable!
